node.text: Now I know why we need to put salt into cucumbers! 😁

🥔 This Japanese potato Salad taste just like the ones at Japanese restaurants! It’s better when you serve it cold🥔 Did I mention how easy it is to make this as well!⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Ingredients for potato salad:⁣⁣⁣
❤️500g potatoes, peeled and cut into cubes⁣⁣⁣
❤️100g carrots, peeled and cut into tiny cubes⁣⁣⁣
❤️100g Japanese cucumber, sliced thinly⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Ingredients for dressing:⁣⁣⁣
❤️1/3 cup Japanese kewpie mayo⁣⁣⁣
❤️1 tbsp rice vinegar⁣⁣⁣
❤️2 tsp sugar⁣⁣⁣
❤️Sprinkle of salt (to taste)⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Steps:⁣⁣⁣
1)Rub the cucumbers with salt and set aside for 30mins (This helps make them crunchy)⁣⁣⁣
2)Boil potatoes and carrots in a pot of water for about 20mins⁣
3)Drain the potatoes and carrots well and use a masher to slightly mash⁣⁣⁣
4)Mix all the dressing ingredients together and add them to the mash potatoes⁣⁣⁣
5)Squeeze water out of the cucumbers and add them to the potatoes ⁣⁣⁣
6)Add a pinch of salt if desired⁣
7)Refrigerate and serve cold⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
